      <title>三月份反弹期间加密货币交易量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/crypto-trading-volume-reached-all-time-high-during-march-rally-ccdata-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 CCData 的数据，3 月份集中交易所的加密货币现货和衍生品交易量几乎翻了一番，达到 9.1 万亿美元的历史新高，而比特币则创下了历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/crypto-trading-volume-reached-all-time-high-during-march-rally-ccdata-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:47:58 GMT</pubDate>
